H0.text: Whole milk is the liquid most likely to contain a dissolved gas.

H1.text: House paint is the liquid most likely to contain a dissolved gas.

H2.text: Mud puddle is the liquid most likely to contain a dissolved gas.

H3.text: Carbonated soda is a liquid that most likely contains a dissolved gas.

A4.text: Carbonation levels range up to 5 volumes of CO2 per liquid volume.

A5.text: The dissolution of carbon dioxide (CO2) in a liquid, gives rise to effervescence or fizz.
